javac.comp

类 TransTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • javac.tree.JCTree.Visitor
      • javac.tree.TreeTranslator
        • javac.comp.TransTypes

  • public class TransTypes
extends TreeTranslator
    This pass translates Generic Java to conventional Java.

    This is NOT part of any supported API. If you write code that depends on this, you do so at your own risk. This code and its internal interfaces are subject to change or deletion without notice.

        public JCTree.JCExpression coerce(Env<AttrContext> env,
                                  JCTree.JCExpression tree,
                                  Type target)
        Construct an attributed tree to coerce an expression to some erased target type, unless the expression is already assignable to that type. If target type is a constant type, use its base type instead.
        参数:
        tree - The expression tree.
        target - The target type.
